Genres: Action | Drama | Romance
Release date(s) 9 August 2013
Boss is a 2013 Bengali romantic Action film directed by choreographer Baba Yadav marking his directorial debut.The film is the remake of Telugu Blockbuster film Business Man starring Mahesh Babu and Kajal agarwal. The film is produced under the banner of Reliance Entertainment and Grassroot Entertainment Pvt. Ltd. The film stars Jeet and Subhasree Ganguly in lead roles and Chiranjeet Chatterjee in supporting roles.


